data.description: Fantastic opportunity in gated Goldcrest Estates 55+ Community!  Bright and airy 3 bedroom/2 bath split bedroom home features vaulted ceilings, skylights, gas fireplace, and large covered patio.  The master bathroom includes a dual vanity and an upgraded walk in shower/tub combination. 3rd bedroom doubles as an office with beautiful French doors and closet with built in shelves. New roof 2023. Come enjoy a centrally located home with easy access to shopping, medical facilities, parks, and highway.  This home offers plenty of storage and a large community club house complete with workout/weight room, pool, hot tub, library, and community clubhouse.  RV/Boat parking available.  Home is on leased land with rent payments of $410/month. No additional HOA dues.
